We collect personal data only to the extent necessary for the development and testing of the app. This may include account details, usage data, and error reports. Please note that the app is in a developmental phase, and any data collected may be subject to change.

2. Data Usage
We may use your data to identify issues, improve app performance, and troubleshoot errors. By using the app, you consent to the collection and use of data for these purposes.

